snippet.title: Durango - E3 2017 Teaser
snippet.description:
Durango, the next evolution of persistent open-world MMORPGs, will be at E3 2017 as it prepares for launch later this year! Pioneer and settle Durango’s massive and dynamic primitive world teeming with dinosaurs and tribal warfare!

To learn more, visit the official Durango website: https://durango.nexon.com

Follow the latest news on the Durango Facebook page: https://www.facebook.com/playdurango/
